profile:
Since 2009, Canadoor Door Systems has been bringing professionalism to the garage door industry. To ensure we perform every job to the highest standard, whether you need a garage door repair or installation, our technicians undergo a rigorous training process until we’re confident they are ready to enter the field.

We provide service across Ontario, with showrooms in Sudbury, Barrie, Bolton, and Thunder Bay, where you can meet our team and browse our selection of garage doors. Whether you’re a homeowner in need of a garage door repair, new installation or a business looking for preventative maintenance on your commercial properties, we can help.

profile:
Nordoors Sudbury proudly serving the City of Greater Sudbury and area, specializes in sales and repair of residential, commercial, and industrial garage doors, electric operators and dock levelers. Our team offers personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program. 

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as a variety of accessories for your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door. We are a proud member of the Sudbury Construction Association and the Sudbury Chamber of Commerce.
